CBRE Capital Markets is thrilled to be favored with instructions for the sale of 215 Grote Street, Adelaide currently under a long-term lease to national furniture retailer Early Settler. 215 Grote Street is exceptionally well-situated to the West of the Adelaide CBD, in an established commercial precinct in very close proximity to Chinatown, Adelaide Central Markets, West Terrace & just 900m* from the Adelaide BioMedical Precinct.

Underpinning the exceptional location is the underlying land value with a total site area of 2,787sqm* within a flexible zoning. The building consists of three levels with varied improvements including showroom, offices, warehousing & café.

We further highlight the below key features of the property which is the perfect definition of an ‘invest now, develop later’ property:

- Net rental of $531,726pa*
- Leased to ESR Group Holdings Pty Ltd trading as Early Settler with over 50 stores across Australia & New Zealand
- 5-year lease term expiring 31st October 2024 with further 5-year option
- Site area of 2,787sqm* and GLA of 3,685sqm*
- Flexible Capital City zoning in the City of Adelaide allowing development up to 53m*
- Two Certificates of Title with three street frontages 
- CPI rental increases annually
- Redevelopment Clause within the lease with 18-month notice period
- Tenant pays all outgoings including Land Tax on a single-holding basis

For Sale by Expressions of Interest closing Friday 21st June 2019 at 4:00pm (ACST)

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
10 Sydney Place, offers a perfect owner occupier or storage opportunity. Located just off Halifax Street, 10 Sydney Place benefits from the surrounding infrastructure including public transport along King William Street which is approximately 250 metres away. 

The “City South” precinct is an area which is an ever-growing community that has expanded around the abundance of townhouses and apartment living. High-end cafes, restaurants and markets are within 500 metres of walking and have seen the gentrification of the area over the past few years. The property offers the following features;

- 160 sqm* open and secure garage space
- Additional 27 sqm* of neat front-end office 
- 227 sqm* of land holding 
- Existing development approval for boutique 6 dwelling project
- Zoned City Living (Policy 32) in the City of Adelaide

FOR SALE BY PRIVATE TREATY - $825,000 (exc GST)

The property located at 53-67 Hindmarsh Square occupies a fantastic location overlooking Hindmarsh Square and is situated next to The Mantra Hotel to the south and Conservatory to the north. The tenancy formally occupied by the RAA is currently fitted with air conditioning, carpets throughout and a number of partitioned offices.

The property consists of ground floor accommodation of approximately 840 sqm.

The property lends itself to be sub-divided to provide 2 or 3 retail tenancies of between 185 sqm to 360 sqm. The tenancies would suit a number of uses including office, retail and restaurant use.

Enquire today to avoid disappointment.

Lease Term: 10 years
Option: 5 years
Available: Immediately
